            { "text" : "### Prerequisites\n\nThis text will explore the concept of addition in greater depth. As such, we recommend reviewing the previous chapters, along with their respective prerequisites",
              "source" : [ 
                  { "type": 1,
                    "uuid": "b5efc8f9-c268-430f-9681-7a43848ee48e",
                    "text": "History Tracers Team, First Steps",
                    "date" :  {"type" : "gregory", "year" : "2024", "month" : "-1", "day" : "-1" }}
               ],
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
